parameters:
I am the one who will be serving from today. I have come for the
meeting and interview with the young lady.
\SE[0]... Hmmm. So you're the new person.

\SE[21]Ahaha... Take it easy on me... By the way, is there any
criteria for passing?\ I have confidence in being able to handle
anything to a certain extent...

\SE[14]... Did Father say something to you? \SE[4] There aren't
any special conditions. \. I will be observing you...

\SE[4]This person can't even do such simple things... \.
\SE[59]And yet, they're an adult but dumber than me... \.
\SE[45]I wonder when this person will ever learn... \.
\SE[33]...I dislike people like that who are so boring.

\SE[2] (...I see. \. It's the stress that comes with being an
excellent child, huh.... \!\SE[25] Well, I might be a bit cheeky
myself.)

\SE\SE[15]In that case, there's no problem. \. I am resourceful,
\. intelligent, \. and interesting. \!\SE[15]I will never bore
the young lady!
\SE[14]I-Is that so... You seem very confident...

\SE[14]Well then, let's start the interview right away!
\SE[0]What should I do to prove myself? ....Do you have any
specific requests from the young lady?
\SE[44]Hide and seek... I want to play.

\SE[12] (Oh, you came to an unexpected place... You have a
childish side, huh.)

\SE[58]D-Don't get any strange misunderstandings...!
\SE[55]Playing hide and seek during the interview is not a waste.
It's not like I want to play or anything.

\SE\SE[2]You can remember the structure of the mansion, and you
can also assess your observational skills and resourcefulness in
an unfamiliar environment. \SE[2]...right? That's how it is,
isn't it?

\SE[58] (Hmm... that's true,\. there might be some truth to that.
\!\SE[57] This child's words have a strange persuasiveness to
them, don't they...)

\SE[59]And besides, if it's someone who knows the structure....
\SE[40]They'll find me right away, and it won't be
interesting....

\SE[16] (Oh my, is that your true feelings? \!\SE[45] Hehe... I
definitely want to pass this.
\SE[1]Yes, understood. I will find her as soon as possible.

\SE[12]If you can do it, give it a try! \SE[13]Starting from now,
we'll begin the search in 10 minutes! \SE[12]Alright!
\SE[12]Absolutely no cheating allowed!

\SE[15]Hehe... She went off. \SE[11]This is a serious match...
isn't it? Let's show them our serious adult side...!

W-Wow, the mansion is huge...! Are we going to search for the
young lady from here...!?

Th-This won't get us anywhere....! In times like this, it's time
for questioning! Solving a case always starts with a diligent
step!

Oh, there's a senior maid in a good place. Excuse me! I would
like to ask you a few questions!!

...Huh? Is questioning against the rules? You can't say it
because you'll get fired if you reveal it...?

I see! So the workplace has a strong compliance! It seems like a
good place, I feel relieved!
